long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a free add-on for Chrome Browser where the primary target is to set a background from our selective Military images gallery powered by Unsplash in your Chrome Browser default new tab. We are actually changing your Chrome browser default new tab page. Also as an added feature, we are giving you an easy way to search your desired information, images, video, and more through Bing search. There is also a Digital Clock in new tabs where you can check your current location time in 12 hour/ 24-hour format according to your preference.
